            </ul>
            <p class="resources-contact"><strong>Municipal Law Enforcement:</strong> Contact through the Town's main line for licensing inquiries.</p>
          </div>

          <p>The proposed bylaw was presented in Staff Report 2025-0144 at the September 9, 2025 General Committee Meeting. Check Council meeting records for the final approved version and any amendments.</p>

