            <h3>Planning to Host in Caledon?</h3>
            <p>The 300 license cap means early movers have the advantage. We help property owners in Caledon, Bolton, and Caledon East navigate compliance, optimize listings, and maximize revenue. Whether you're going for an STR license or pivoting to mid-term rentals, we handle everything while you collect rent.</p>
